#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Converting dangerous documents to safe PDFs using Dangerzone\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Convertir documents perillosos en PDF segurs mitjançant Dangerzone\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"When you receive untrusted documents, for example, email attachments, "
"*[Dangerzone](https://dangerzone.rocks/)* allows you to convert them into "
"safe PDFs before opening."
msgstr ""
"Quan rebeu documents no fiables, per exemple, fitxers adjunts de correu "
"electrònic, *[Dangerzone](https://dangerzone.rocks/)* us permet convertir-"
"los en fitxers PDF segurs abans d'obrir-los."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*Dangerzone* is particularly useful for journalists who might receive dangerous\n"
"documents from anonymous sources or download them from the Internet.\n"
msgstr ""
"*Dangerzone* és especialment útil per als periodistes que reben documents\n"
"potencialment perillosos de fonts anònimes o els baixen d'Internet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"tip\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"tip\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "<p><i>Dangerzone</i> is created by <a href=\"https://freedom.press/\">Freedom of\n"
#| "the Press Foundation</a>, a non-profit that protects public-interest\n"
#| "journalism. Edward Snowden and Laura Poitras are on its Board of Directors.</p>\n"
msgid ""
"<p><i>Dangerzone</i> is created by <a href=\"https://freedom.press/\">Freedom of\n"
"the Press Foundation</a>, a nonprofit that protects public-interest\n"
"journalism. Edward Snowden and Laura Poitras are on its Board of Directors.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p><i>Dangerzone</i> ha estat creat per <a href=\"https://freedom.press/\">Freedom of\n"
"the Press Foundation</a>, una organització sense ànim de lucre que protegeix el periodisme\n"
"d'interès públic. Edward Snowden i Laura Poitras formen part del seu consell d'administració.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"You can install *Dangerzone* in Tails using the [[Additional Software|"
"additional_software]] feature."
msgstr ""
"Podeu instal·lar *Dangerzone* a Tails mitjançant la funcionalitat de "
"[[Programari Addicional|additional_software]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We are not including *Dangerzone* in Tails only because it would be too big "
"(over 1 GB), but we highly recommend it."
msgstr ""
"No incloem *Dangerzone* a Tails només perquè seria massa gran (més d'1 GB), "
"però el recomanem."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Learn more about [how *Dangerzone* works](https://dangerzone.rocks/about/)."
msgstr ""
"Més informació sobre [com funciona *Dangerzone*](https://dangerzone.rocks/"
"about/)."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toc levels=2]]\n"
msgstr "[[!toc levels=2]]\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Supported formats"
msgstr "Formats compatibles"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Dangerzone* works on many file formats, including:\n"
msgstr "*Dangerzone* funciona en molts formats de fitxer, com ara:\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- PDFs"
msgstr "- PDF"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- *Microsoft Office* documents, such as .docx, .xlsx, and .pptx"
msgstr "- Documents de *Microsoft Office*, com ara .docx, .xlsx i .pptx"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- *LibreOffice* documents, such as .odt and .ods"
msgstr "- Documents del *LibreOffice*, com ara .odt i .ods"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Images, such as .jpg, .gif, .svg, .tiff, and .png"
msgstr "- Fitxers d'imatge, com ara .jpeg, .png i .gif"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- EPUB ebooks"
msgstr "- Llibres electrònics EPUB"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Differences between *Dangerzone* and *Metadata Cleaner*"
msgstr "Diferències entre *Dangerzone* i el *Netejador de Metadades*"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails also includes [[*Metadata Cleaner*|doc/sensitive_documents/metadata]] "
"to clean files, but the use cases for *Dangerzone* and *Metadata Cleaner* "
"are very different."
msgstr ""
"Tails també inclou el [[*Netejador de Metadades*|doc/sensitive_documents/"
"metadata]] per netejar fitxers, però els casos d'ús de *Dangerzone* i del "
"*Netejador de Metadades* són molt diferents."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "We recommend that you use:"
msgstr "Us recomanem que utilitzeu:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"*Metadata Cleaner* to [[remove metadata from your files|doc/"
"sensitive_documents/metadata]] before you publish or share them."
msgstr ""
"El *Netejador de Metadades* per [[eliminar metadades dels vostres fitxers|"
"doc/sensitive_documents/metadata]] abans de publicar-los o compartir-los."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- *Dangerzone* to sanitize untrusted documents shared with you by others."
msgstr ""
"- *Dangerzone* per desinfectar documents no fiables compartits per altres "
"persones."

